    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">JOCASTE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">IOCASTE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="663">
OLympe, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">va&#160;t’en </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C">va-t’en </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">va-t-en </rdg>
      </app>
voir ce funeste 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">spectacle, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">spectacle. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="664">
Va voir si leur fureur n’a point 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">trouvé </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">trouué </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">d’obstacle, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">d’obstacle. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="665">
Si rien n’a pû toucher 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">l’un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">l’vn </rdg>
      </app>
ou l’autre 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">party, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">party&#160;; </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">parti&#160;; </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="666">
On dit qu’à ce dessein 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Ménecée </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Menecée </rdg>
      </app>
est 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">sorty. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">sorti. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>OLYMPE.</speaker>
<l n="667">
Je ne 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">sçay </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">sçai </rdg>
      </app>
quel dessein animoit son courage, </l>

<l n="668">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Une </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Vne </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">heroyque </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">heroïque </rdg>
      </app>
ardeur brilloit sur son 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">visage, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">visage&#160;; </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="669">
Mais vous 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #D #E">devez, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">deuez, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">devés, </rdg>
      </app>
Madame, esperer jusqu’au bout. </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">JOCASTE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">IOCASTE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="670">
Va tout voir, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">chere </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">cher </rdg>
      </app>
Olympe, &amp; me viens dire tout. </l>

<l n="671">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Esclaircy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #D">Eclaircy </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">Eclairci </rdg>
      </app>
promptement ma triste inquietude. </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #C #D #E">OLYMPE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">OLIMPE . </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="672">
Mais vous dois-je laisser en cette solitude&#160;? </l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#C #D #E">JOCASTE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A #B">IOCASTE. </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="673">
Va, je veux estre seule en l’estat où 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">ie </rdg>
      </app>
suis, </l>

<l n="674">
Si pourtant on peut l’estre 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #E">avecque </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">auecque </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">avec </rdg>
      </app>
tant d’ennuis. </l>

